All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Cloneable, Block, ContentBlock, org.jfree.ui.Drawable
public class SymbolAxis extends NumberAxis implements Serializable
A standard linear value axis that replaces integer values with symbols.
Author:
Anthony Boulestreau

      plotArea - the area within which the chart should be drawn.
      dataArea - the area within which the plot should be drawn (a subset of the drawArea).
